{"tid":705145,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"警︰中途加入7.1遊行或違法","createTime":"2018-06-17T01:33:55.000Z","updateTime":"2018-06-17T06:55:21.000Z","uid":25558,"like":5,"dislike":22,"uniUserReply":13,"replies":[{"pid":"08cbe215aa157946c9278970c61230594e7c6a74","tid":705145,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-17T01:33:56.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/daily/article/20180617/20423002\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20180617%2F20423002&d=Bmpm5q5QS7AG2K8WhxIbDOPnIAwyWqphGIcg0J4V%2Buw%3D&h=05c55315\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20180617%2F20423002&h=14b659c3\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/daily/article/20180617/20423002</a><br />\n<br />\n2018年06月17日 <br />\n<br />\n警︰中途加入7.1遊行或違法<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/apple-photos/apple/20180617/large/17la6p6.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fapple-photos%2Fapple%2F20180617%2Flarge%2F17la6p6.jpg&h=a9de9dbf&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n【本報訊】警方就7.1遊行向民陣發出不反對通知書，但要求出發地點改為維園草坪，而非民陣要求的銅鑼灣東角道。警務處長盧偉聰（圖）昨回應指，據警方過往經驗，認為維園才是最適合人群聚集的地方，「東角道車多人多，同埋係星期日，根本上係唔適合咁大型嘅聚集」，重申警方要求更改地點是為公共安全和市民的人身安全，籲市民聽從指示，從維園出發。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n「有可能參與非法集會」<br />\n<br />\n民陣籲參與7.1遊行市民自行在東角道加入，盧就稱市民要慎重考慮，「因為任何參與呢啲活動嘅人，係有可能參與非法集會」，強調市民若在其他地方中途加入，只會擾亂遊行和造成不必要混亂。<br />\n<br />\n民陣召集人葉志衍則指，據過往經驗，若遊行人士、傳媒、警方聚集在草坪亦會構成混亂。民陣亦向警方建議過其他遊行起點，如東角道、公民廣場，但遭拒絕。盧指遊行人士若從其他地點出發，或涉非法集會，葉指民陣已做好準備，也會向參與者解釋清楚。<br />\n<br />\n民陣於去年12月向康文署申請使用維園6個足球場作遊行起點，惟在今年4月接到回覆稱已批予慶委會作展覽，所以不能在7.1當天使用維園足球場。民陣申請不反對通知書時，估計今年會有1,500人在起點參與7.1集會。<br />\n<br />\n■記者甘泳楠  <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n上一則<br />\n上一則<br />\n泛民：提不信任動議以儆效尤<br />\n<br />\n下一則<br />\n下一則<br />\n累病人重複打針　港怡遭勸喻"},{"pid":"79ad94e573ec32337a254c21969c0acd3f6929f5","tid":705145,"uid":26156,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-17T01:39:22.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"272f12682a48a6d4d829a9ea59ccd5900cbb0102","tid":705145,"uid":20867,"like":4,"dislike":4,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-17T01:42:28.000Z","msg":"連差佬都收到order要出口幫民陣穀人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9caefa9de7b8c362a5f4c6a7cefa99521b8e1112","tid":705145,"uid":44454,"like":13,"dislike":1,"score":12,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-17T01:48:17.000Z","msg":"之前連燈仲鄧女鐵騎車死可憐，警察冇一個係無辜<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8e96ad0007048bdb51442317521597ec6e18916b","tid":705145,"uid":63154,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-17T01:49:19.000Z","msg":"大中華膠遊行籌款show，今年應該創新低"},{"pid":"8a41cf88d4c5eea7643fb48e948eeb00d0699ff3","tid":705145,"uid":15711,"like":3,"dislike":7,"score":-4,"quote":{"pid":"9caefa9de7b8c362a5f4c6a7cefa99521b8e1112","tid":705145,"uid":44454,"like":13,"dislike":1,"score":12,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-17T01:48:17.000Z","msg":"之前連燈仲鄧女鐵騎車死可憐，警察冇一個係無辜<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-17T01:52:24.000Z","msg":"嘩，恥笑下死人就係抗爭左，連登仔勇無真係好易做"},{"pid":"a784e7ef601f75e3479d98c61d0686349075c4f2","tid":705145,"uid":34103,"like":0,"dislike":5,"score":-5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-17T02:42:42.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"f3866be64b98c70510e202510c5af90f435144d6","tid":705145,"uid":15711,"like":0,"dislike":4,"score":-4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-17T03:38:45.000Z","msg":"車，連登仔都係用鍵盤抗爭，遊行關佢地鬼事咩"},{"pid":"2f8dbc3e342880bbafad74f779b94f8cd5c57141","tid":705145,"uid":93043,"like":0,"dislike":3,"score":-3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-17T03:45:24.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"0b693efece91b6fdded2a0c4f7f85813ac45065f","tid":705145,"uid":93043,"like":1,"dislike":4,"score":-3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-17T03:46:15.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"4f23ecc1416b